{
  "ticker": "600219",
  "name": "Shandong Nanshan Aluminium Co.,Ltd.",
  "country": "CN",
  "exchange": "XSHG",
  "sector": "Basic Materials",
  "industry": "Aluminum",
  "currency": "CNY",
  "website": "https://www.600219.com.cn",
  "description": "Shandong Nanshan Aluminium Co.,Ltd. engages in the aluminum processing business worldwide. The company offers upstream products, such as power generation, alumina, aluminum alloy ingots, and aluminum foil, as well as downstream products, including aluminum sheets and strips, which consist of automotive sheets, aviation sheets, and can materials; and industrial and building aluminum profiles. It also engages in the production of various aluminum alloy hot-rolled coils and new alloy products; research and development of high-tech projects and technology transfer; sale of building materials; laboratory testing of materials and its products; processing and refining bauxite; medical business; research, development, production, and sale of aviation and aerospace components; and metal scrap and shavings processing. In addition, the company is involved in the recycling of industrial waste metals; sale of non-ferrous metal alloys; health consultation services, engineering management services, and human resource management services; non-ferrous metal milling; research, development, production, and sale of chlor-alkali chemical products; trade of chemical products; sale of photovoltaic power generation; and sale of metal materials and ores. Its products are used in aviation, automotive, rail transportation, shipbuilding, energy, petrochemical, container, industrial profiles, high-quality civil profiles, high-end system doors and windows, containers, food packaging, battery foil, and deep aluminum processing fields. The company was formerly known as Shandong Nanshan Industrial Co., Ltd. and changed its name to Shandong Nanshan Aluminium Co.,Ltd. in March 2006. Shandong Nanshan Aluminium Co.,Ltd. was incorporated in 1993 and is headquartered in Longkou, China.",
